name: Executive-Jr.-Suite--Executive-Jr.-Suite-Living-Room---Partial-View
caption: Executive Jr. Suite Living Room - Partial View
description: The living room includes a sleeper sofa, arm chair, window, tv, and small dining table.
alt: The living room provides a sleeper sofa on the back wall with a glass coffee table in front of it. To the right, there is a standing lamp. A TV is suspended on the wall to the right of the window, above a dresser. Opposite the TV is a round dining table.
